WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:04.000
ST-Firm inawasilisha.

00:04.000 --> 00:08.000
Jenga… jenga… Inaendeshwa na SSOS.

00:08.000 --> 00:12.000
Jifunze. Jenga. Shiriki. Wezesha.

00:12.000 --> 00:22.000
Ravine hadi Duniani! Twende pamoja!
Wanachama 29 wanaoshiriki mtandaoni.

00:22.000 --> 00:22.900
Maarifa yanakuwa kitu unachoweza kutumia.

00:22.900 --> 00:24.200
Akili bandia, Python,
automation na cybersecurity.

00:24.200 --> 00:25.350
Ujasiriamali, uongozi,
elimu ya fedha na uendelevu.

00:25.350 --> 00:26.000
Maarifa yanakuwa uwezo.

00:26.000 --> 00:28.900
Nilitoka Eldama na ndoto mfukoni.

00:28.900 --> 00:31.500
Moi International, Mombasa runway.
Safari inaanza.

00:31.500 --> 00:33.300
Ndege ikapaa! Siku mpya inaanza.

00:33.300 --> 00:34.300
Kenya hadi Deutschland.

00:34.300 --> 00:35.600
Tumetua Berlin.

00:35.600 --> 00:38.100
Nimetua Berlin. Sura mpya inaanza.

00:38.100 --> 00:41.700
Berlin ikawa warsha.
Tunajenga mifumo huru.

00:41.700 --> 00:43.000
Safari ikawa mfumo.

00:43.000 --> 00:47.000
Sema SSOS. Akili huru.
Mwendelezo wa biashara.

00:47.000 --> 00:49.550
Akädemie.

00:49.550 --> 00:50.300
Jifunze. Jenga. Shiriki. Wezesha.

00:50.300 --> 00:53.300
Maarifa yanakuwa uhandisi.
Uhandisi unaunganisha akili.

00:53.300 --> 00:56.500
Akili inaimarisha shughuli halisi.
Shughuli zinatengeneza thamani halisi.

00:56.500 --> 00:58.000
Thamani inawarudia watu na kujenga kizazi kijacho.

00:58.000 --> 01:05.000
Taking Ravine to the World
and bringing the World to Eldama Ravine.

01:05.000 --> 01:10.000
Engineer Saigut Julius Kipkorir—AKA KingKunta.
